OL,3,CNottingham Forest lose appeal against
OL,4,C#750k fine for referee criticism
OL,6,FThe post said: "We warned the PGMOL
OL,7,Fthat the VAR is a Luton fan before the
OL,8,Fgame but they didn't change him."
OL,10,FA regulatory commission issued a #750k
OL,11,Ffine last October, with Forest
OL,12,Fimmediately indicating their intention
OL,13,Fto appeal, arguing the punishment was
OL,14,F"disproportionate".
OL,16,FThe Football Association had been
OL,17,Fseeking a punishment of at least #1
OL,18,Fmillion for what it described as an
OL,19,F"egregious, direct and public attack"
OL,20,Fon Attwell and an attack on referees
OL,21,Fin general "on an unparalleled scale".
