OL,3,CNottingham Forest lose appeal against
OL,4,C#750k fine for referee criticism
OL,6,FComments made by manager Nuno Espirito
OL,7,FSanto and defender Neco Williams in
OL,8,Frelation to the officiating at the
OL,9,FEverton game also resulted in
OL,10,Fsanctions, with Nuno given a suspended
OL,11,Fone-match touchline ban, a #40,000
OL,12,Ffine and a warning as to his future
OL,13,Fconduct, and Williams warned and fined
OL,14,F#24,000.
OL,16,FForest owner Evangelos Marinakis had
OL,17,Fto serve a five-match stadium ban
OL,18,Fearlier this season after he was found
OL,19,Fguilty of spitting in the direction of
OL,20,Fofficials following the club's match
OL,21,Fagainst Fulham on September 28.
